    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-1a' );" name="004-1a" class="pb">[004-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　禹貢㑹箋卷四</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　翰林院檢討徐文靖撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:238'>海岱及淮惟徐州<span class='krp-note'>周合其地/于青州</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='238:261'>　蔡傳曰徐州之域東至海南至淮北至岱而西不言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='261:284'>　濟者岱之陽濟東為徐岱之北濟東為青言濟不足</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='284:310'>　以辨故畧之也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按爾雅濟東曰徐州注云自濟東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='310:333'>　至海若言濟不足以辨此何以單言濟也故知言淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='333:359'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-1b' );" name="004-1b" class="pb">[004-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='359:382'>　以别於青不事并言濟也葢海岱青徐所同淮海徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='382:395'>　揚所同海岱及淮乃徐耳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='395:408'>淮沂其乂<span class='krp-note'>乂史/作治</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='408:431'>　蔡傳曰淮見導水曾氏曰淮之源出於豫之境至揚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='431:454'>　徐之間始大其泛濫為患尤在於徐故淮之治於徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='454:477'>　言之也沂水地志出泰山郡葢縣艾山今沂州沂水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='477:503'>　縣也南至於下邳西南而入於泗<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按金氏曰淮出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='503:526'>　今唐州桐栢山行千七百里至海州入海水經注曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='526:552'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-2a' );" name="004-2a" class="pb">[004-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='552:575'>　鄭氏云沂出沂山或云臨樂山水有二源南源所導</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='575:599'>　世謂之柞泉北水所𤼵俗謂之窮魚泉俱東南合成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='599:622'>　一川至下邳縣北西流分為二水一水於城北西南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='622:645'>　入泗一水逕城東屈從縣南亦注泗謂之小沂水左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='645:668'>　傳隱六年公㑹齊侯盟於艾杜注泰山牟縣東南有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='668:691'>　艾山沂水所出即是山也鄭氏曰沂出沂山今青州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='691:708'>　沂水縣山沂水出其西接臨朐縣界</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='708:731'>　蔡傳曰曾氏云徐州水以沂名者非一酈道元謂水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='731:757'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-2b' );" name="004-2b" class="pb">[004-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='757:780'>　出尼丘山西北過魯之雩門亦謂之沂水出太公武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='780:809'>　陽之冠石山<span class='krp-note'>太公誤當/是太山</span>亦謂之沂水而沂水之大則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='809:835'>　出於泰山也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按昭二十五年左傳平子請待於沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='835:858'>　上杜氏曰魯城南自有沂水此小沂也地理志沂水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='858:881'>　出泰山葢縣臨樂子山南至下邳入泗過郡五行六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='881:904'>　百里此大沂水也郡國志琅邪臨沂縣有洛水注之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='904:927'>　水出太山南武陽之冠石山是出冠石者洛水非沂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='927:950'>　水也世以其注沂亦或謂之小沂水是徐州之水以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='950:976'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-3a' );" name="004-3a" class="pb">[004-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='976:1000'>　沂名者非一也唐孔氏曰乂訓治也淮出桐栢山𤼵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='1000:1023'>　源逺矣於此州言之者淮水至此而大為害尤甚喜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='1023:1034'>　得其治故於此記之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='1034:1057'>　蔡傳曰徐之水有泗有汶有汴有漷而獨以淮沂言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1057:1080'>　者徐之川莫大於淮淮乂則自泗而下凡為川者可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1080:1103'>　知矣徐之浸莫大於沂沂乂則自沭而下凡為浸者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1103:1129'>　可知矣<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按日記曰汴水出滎陽縣大周山合京索</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1129:1152'>　須鄭四水東南至中牟縣北入於黄河泗水出泗水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1152:1178'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-3b' );" name="004-3b" class="pb">[004-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1178:1202'>　縣陪尾山其水四源並𤼵循城北八里始合為一西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1202:1225'>　流至曲阜經嵫陽城東五里與沂水合漷水在滕縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1225:1248'>　東北七十里出東海合鄉西南經魯國至高平湖陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1248:1271'>　縣入泗沭水源出沂山自莒州西北流入州境㑹諸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1271:1294'>　澗水南經馬陵山入郯城縣注於淮泗徐士彰曰日</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1294:1317'>　記所録乃兗州之泉而非徐州之水其所謂泗則今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1317:1340'>　泗水縣之泗而非泗州之泗也然地志謂東莞術水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1340:1368'>　<span class='krp-note'>即沭/水也</span>至下邳入泗郭璞謂泗水至下相入淮水經謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1368:1394'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-4a' );" name="004-4a" class="pb">[004-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1394:1417'>　漷水至湖陸縣入泗獲水出汴水至彭城縣北東入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1417:1440'>　泗東莞今青州臨朐下邳今邳州下相今宿遷湖陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1440:1463'>　故城今徐州沛縣烏在盡為兗州之水而非徐州之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1463:1468'>　水也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1468:1474'>蒙羽其藝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1474:1497'>　蔡傳曰蒙山地志在泰山郡䝉隂縣西南今沂州費</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1497:1520'>　縣也羽山地志在東海郡祝其縣南今海州朐山縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1520:1546'>　也藝者言可種藝也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按哀十七年公㑹齊侯盟於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1546:1572'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-4b' );" name="004-4b" class="pb">[004-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1572:1595'>　蒙杜預曰蒙在東莞蒙隂縣西今蒙山在蒙隂縣南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1595:1618'>　四十里其陽為費縣隂為蒙隂縣也連山易曰有崇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1618:1641'>　伯鯀伏於羽山之野寰宇記曰羽山俗呼懲父山漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1641:1664'>　志在祝其唐武德八年省祝其入懷仁金大定七年</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1664:1687'>　改懷仁縣為贛榆今屬淮安府海州其藝孔傳曰二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1687:1709'>　山已可種藝正義曰詩云藝之荏菽故藝為種也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1709:1723'>大野既豬<span class='krp-note'>史記豬/作都</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1723:1746'>　蔡傳曰大野澤名地志在山陽郡鉅野縣北今濟州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1746:1772'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-5a' );" name="004-5a" class="pb">[004-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1772:1798'>　鉅野縣也鉅即大也水蓄而復流者謂之豬<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按左</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1798:1821'>　傳哀十七年西狩於大野杜預曰鉅野縣東北大澤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1821:1844'>　是也鉅野界徐之西兗之東南北三百里東西百餘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1844:1867'>　里故周禮職方兗州澤藪曰大野王順渠曰南旺湖</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1867:1890'>　在汶上縣西南縈洄計百十餘里而㑹通漕河貫乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1890:1913'>　其中湖界為二西湖廣衍倍於東湖是南旺即古大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1913:1932'>　野無疑一統志湖在汶上縣西南二十里</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1932:1955'>　蔡傳曰何承天曰鉅野廣大南導洙泗北連清濟徐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1955:1981'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-5b' );" name="004-5b" class="pb">[004-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1981:2008'>　之有濟於是乎見又鄆州中都西南亦有大野陂<span class='krp-note'>中/都</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='2008:2040'>　<span class='krp-note'>今東平州/汶上縣</span>或皆古大野之地也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按春秋莊公十八</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='2040:2063'>　年夏公追戎於濟西左傳僖三十一年分曹地東傅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='2063:2086'>　於濟則徐之有濟可知孔傳水所停曰豬馬云水所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='2086:2095'>　停止深者曰豬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2095:2101'>東原厎平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2101:2124'>　蔡傳曰東原在徐之西北而謂之東者以在濟東故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2124:2147'>　也東平國在景帝亦謂濟東國云益知大野東原所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2147:2173'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-6a' );" name="004-6a" class="pb">[004-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2173:2199'>　以志濟也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按漢宣帝甘露二年為東平國景帝中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2199:2222'>　六年濟東國也水經濟水故瀆又北右合洪水酈注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2222:2245'>　曰上承鉅野薛訓渚厯澤西北渚又北逕闞鄉城西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2245:2268'>　郡國志東平陸有闞亭又北濟瀆合自渚迄於北口</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2268:2291'>　一百二十里名曰洪水故張華博物志曰兗州東平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2291:2319'>　郡即尚書之東原也<span class='krp-note'>今東平/州也</span>孔傳曰致功而地平言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2319:2325'>　可耕也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2325:2332'>厥土赤埴墳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2332:2358'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-6b' );" name="004-6b" class="pb">[004-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2358:2381'>　蔡傳曰土黏曰埴埴膩也周有搏埴之工老氏言埏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2381:2407'>　埴以為器惟土性黏膩細密故可搏可埏也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2407:2430'>　禮草人職赤緹用羊埴壚用豕考工記用土為瓦謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2430:2444'>　之搏埴之工注曰埴土黏也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2444:2450'>草木漸包</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2450:2473'>　蔡傳曰漸進長也如易所謂木漸包叢生也如詩所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2473:2499'>　云如竹包矣言其叢生而積也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按周禮閭師任圃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2499:2522'>　以樹事貢草木草木之貢虞夏已有故禹貢特記其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2522:2548'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-7a' );" name="004-7a" class="pb">[004-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2548:2571'>　漸包也孔傳漸進長包叢生如易彖曰漸進也説卦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2571:2594'>　傳曰巽為木為長為高是也又按木漸蔡傳曰如易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2594:2617'>　所謂木漸象曰山上有木漸漸自為句今讀為木漸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2617:2640'>　可乎爾雅包稹孫炎曰物叢生曰苞齊人名曰稹蔡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2640:2654'>　傳叢生而積積當是稹之譌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2654:2665'>厥田惟上中厥賦中中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2665:2691'>　孔傳曰田第二賦第五<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按周職方青州其川淮泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2691:2714'>　其浸沂沭其榖宜稻麥即禹貢之徐州也周分禹青</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2714:2740'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-7b' );" name="004-7b" class="pb">[004-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2740:2755'>　州東北為幽并禹徐州於青也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2755:2763'>厥貢惟土五色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2763:2786'>　蔡傳曰徐州之土雖赤而五色之土亦間有之故制</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2786:2809'>　以為貢周書作雒曰諸侯受命於周乃建大社於國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2809:2832'>　中其壝東青土南赤土西白土北驪土中央舋以黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2832:2861'>　土將建諸侯鑿取其方面之土<span class='krp-note'>周書方下/有一字</span>包以黄土</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2861:2892'>　苴以白茅以為土封<span class='krp-note'>周書曰以土封/之謂之裂土</span>故曰受削土於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2892:2918'>　周室此貢土五色意亦為是用也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按太康地記曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2918:2944'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-8a' );" name="004-8a" class="pb">[004-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2944:2967'>　城陽姑幕有五色土封諸侯錫之茅土用為社禹時</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2967:2990'>　徐州所貢當即是土也京相璠曰琅邪郡姑幕縣南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2990:3013'>　四十里員亭故魯鄆邑今莒州有姑幕城是也又按</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='3013:3036'>　周書作雒解受則土於周室則法也蔡傳云削土誤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='3036:3042'>羽畎夏翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3042:3065'>　蔡傳曰羽畎羽山之谷也夏翟雉具五色染人之職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3065:3088'>　秋染夏鄭氏曰染夏者染五色也曽氏曰山雉具五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3088:3114'>　色出於羽山之畎則其名山以羽者以此歟<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按孔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3114:3140'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-8b' );" name="004-8b" class="pb">[004-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3140:3163'>　傳曰翟雉名羽中旌旄羽山之谷有之今淮安府贛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3163:3186'>　榆縣山也西界鳯陽府虹縣即漢夏丘縣北齊夏丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3186:3209'>　郡輿地志堯封禹為夏伯邑於此即位徙陽翟周禮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3209:3232'>　内司服掌王后之六服有揄狄闕狄鄭氏曰狄當為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3232:3255'>　翟翟雉名江淮而南青質五色皆備曰揄是羽畎正</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3255:3278'>　夏后受封之地也夏邑在江淮間産此雉故曰夏翟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3278:3301'>　天官夏采注徐州貢夏翟之羽有虞氏以為緌後世</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3301:3324'>　或無故染鳥羽象而用之春官服車五乗孤乗夏篆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3324:3350'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-9a' );" name="004-9a" class="pb">[004-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3350:3373'>　卿乗夏縵皆畫五采以為夏注讀夏為假非也染人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3373:3396'>　染夏即以翟産於夏邑名之非以夏為染采之名也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3396:3419'>　鄭氏曰染五采謂之夏者其色以夏翟為飾染者擬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3419:3438'>　以為深淺之度是以放而名焉則得之矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3438:3444'>嶧陽孤桐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3444:3467'>　蔡傳曰地志東海郡下邳縣有葛嶧山古文以為嶧</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3467:3490'>　山今淮陽軍下邳縣也陽者山南也孤桐特生之桐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3490:3516'>　其材中琴瑟<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按詩魯頌保有鳬繹遂荒徐宅毛傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3516:3542'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-9b' );" name="004-9b" class="pb">[004-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3542:3565'>　曰鳬山也繹山也禹貢嶧陽孤桐孔傳曰孤特也郡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3565:3588'>　國志下邳葛嶧山出名桐一統志山在今邳州城西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3588:3612'>　北六里詩椅桐梓漆爰伐琴瑟陸璣疏桐有青桐赤桐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3612:3636'>　白桐白桐宜琴瑟孤桐殆如龍門之桐百尺無枝者故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3636:3660'>　曰孤桐若以為特生之桐所生無幾焉可定為常貢乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3660:3666'>泗濱浮磬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3666:3689'>　蔡傳曰泗水名出魯國卞縣桃墟西北陪尾山西南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3689:3712'>　過彭城又東南過下邳入淮卞縣今襲慶府泗水縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3712:3739'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-10a' );" name="004-10a" class="pb">[004-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3739:3765'>　也濵水旁也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按水經注泗水逕下邳縣故城西東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3765:3788'>　南流又東南逕淮陽城北臨泗水又東南逕魏陽城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3788:3811'>　北城枕泗州又東逕角城北而東南流注於淮胡三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3811:3834'>　省曰角城在淮水之陽梁後於角城置淮陽郡謂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3834:3850'>　泗口<span class='krp-note'>泗口在今/宿遷縣界</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3850:3873'>　蔡傳曰浮磬石露水濵若浮於水然或曰非也泗濱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3873:3896'>　非必水中泗水之旁近浮者石浮生土中不根著者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3896:3922'>　也今下邳有石磬山或以為古取磬之地<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按左傳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3922:3949'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-10b' );" name="004-10b" class="pb">[004-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3949:3972'>　隱八年公及莒人盟於浮來杜預曰浮來紀邑東莞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3972:3995'>　縣北有邳鄉邳鄉西有公來山號曰邳來間後漢郡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3995:4018'>　國志琅邪東莞有邳鄉有公來山或曰古浮來元和</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='4018:4041'>　郡縣志下邳縣有沂水水經注沂水又東逕浮來之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='4041:4064'>　山在邳鄉西故號曰邳來之間也浮來之水注之是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='4064:4087'>　古者讀邳為浮浮磬即邳磬矣葢當時泗水之濱有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4087:4110'>　浮來之山産此磬石故曰浮磬胡三省注通鑑曰濠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4110:4140'>　州東九十里有浮山山下有穴名浮山洞<span class='krp-note'>九域志泗/州西至濠</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4140:4167'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-11a' );" name="004-11a" class="pb">[004-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4167:4196'>　<span class='krp-note'>州一百七/十五里</span>水經淮水自鍾離縣又東逕浮山今泗州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4196:4219'>　盱眙亦有浮山若以浮生土中為浮磬則浮山亦可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4219:4242'>　謂浮生者乎明堂位叔之離磬世本無句作磬皇氏</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4242:4252'>　曰無句叔之别名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4252:4268'>淮夷蠙珠暨魚<span class='krp-note'>史記作/臮魚</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4268:4294'>　蔡傳曰淮夷淮之夷也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按孔傳曰淮夷二水王肅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4294:4317'>　亦以淮夷為水名鄭氏曰淮夷淮水之夷民也後漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4317:4340'>　東夷傳武乙衰敝東夷寖盛遂分遷淮岱為淮夷所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4340:4367'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-11b' );" name="004-11b" class="pb">[004-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4367:4390'>　由始今禹貢徐州已有淮夷則淮之有夷乆矣魯頌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4390:4413'>　憬彼淮夷來獻其琛毛傳曰淮夷東國在淮浦而夷</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4413:4436'>　行也徐州之稱淮夷者殆以此耳詩記曰徐州在淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4436:4459'>　北徐州有淮夷夷之在北者也詩有曰率彼淮浦省</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4459:4482'>　此徐土是淮北之夷也若在淮南則徐土非聯接之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4482:4487'>　地矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4487:4510'>　蔡傳曰蠙蚌之别名也暨及也珠為服飾魚用祭祀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4510:4536'>　今濠泗楚皆貢淮白魚亦古之遺制歟<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按周官太</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4536:4563'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-12a' );" name="004-12a" class="pb">[004-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4563:4586'>　宰九貢有游貢鄭曰游貢燕好珠璣也又有物貢鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4586:4609'>　曰雜物魚鹽也賈疏曰珠即蠙珠魚即暨魚徐州所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4609:4632'>　貢詩傳曰佩玉上有葱衡下有雙璜衡牙蠙珠以納</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4632:4655'>　其間賈公彦曰蠙蜯也珠出於蜯故言蠙珠鹽鐵論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4655:4678'>　綴以朱蠙是蠙珠並為服飾也蠙説文作班云夏書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4678:4702'>　從賓從虫蠙亦作班宋𢎞曰淮水出班珠珠之有聲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4702:4725'>　者也夏小正二月祭鮪傳曰鮪也者魚之先至者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4725:4748'>　月令季冬始漁乃嘗魚先薦寢廟周禮䱷人職凡祭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4748:4775'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-12b' );" name="004-12b" class="pb">[004-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4775:4798'>　祀賓客共其魚之鱻薧故貢魚也後周太祖本紀曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4798:4821'>　其沿淮州郡淮白魚今後不須進奉是淮白魚之不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4821:4844'>　貢久矣宋志楚州貢苧布泗州貢絹濠州貢糟魚蔡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4844:4863'>　傳以為今濠泗楚皆貢淮白魚不知何据</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4863:4871'>厥篚𤣥纎縞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4871:4895'>　蔡傳曰𤣥赤黑色幣也纎縞皆繒也禮曰素縞麻衣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4895:4925'>　<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0941' title='KR0941' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0941.png'/>而纎記曰縞衣而養老則知纎縞皆繒之名也曽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4925:4948'>　氏曰白經赤緯曰縞黑經白緯曰纎纎也縞也皆去</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4948:4975'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-13a' );" name="004-13a" class="pb">[004-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4975:5002'>　凶即吉之服也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按孔氏曰𤣥黑繒縞白繒纎細也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='5002:5027'>　蔡傳以𤣥為赤黑幣而不以𤣥為色者書有曰篚厥</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='5027:5053'>　𤣥黄𤣥用篚則直以為幣焉可也然𤣥纁璣組何嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5053:5078'>　不以𤣥為色也禮雜記曰委武𤣥縞而后㽔鄭注委</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5078:5103'>　武冠卷也𤣥𤣥冠也縞縞冠也小爾雅繒之精者曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5103:5127'>　縞詩毛傳縞薄繒不染故色白是𤣥與纎縞為二色</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5127:5151'>　也郝氏曰最細曰纎粗白曰縞葢𤣥白二色而纎縞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5151:5181'>　二種祥而縞<img height='20' width='20' alt='&amp;KR0941' title='KR0941' src='https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kanripo/KR-Gaiji/master/images/KR0941.png'/>而纎雖據檀弓以為説然當時制為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5181:5208'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-13b' );" name="004-13b" class="pb">[004-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5208:5226'>　貢篚豈必以去凶即吉之服為常篚乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5226:5243'>浮于淮泗達于河<span class='krp-note'>河説文/作菏</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5243:5266'>　蔡傳曰汳水受陳留浚儀隂溝至蒙為灉水東入於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5266:5289'>　泗則淮泗之達河者以灉至於泗也慎又曰泗受泲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5289:5312'>　水東入淮葢泗水至大野而合泲然則泗之上源自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5312:5338'>　泲亦可以通河也<span class='krp-note'>箋/</span>按説文作達於菏水經菏水又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5338:5361'>　東過胡陸縣南東入於泗水注曰澤水所鍾也尚書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5361:5384'>　浮於淮泗達於河是也日記曰淮入海泗入淮淮泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5384:5411'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-14a' );" name="004-14a" class="pb">[004-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5411:5439'>　不與河通由泗而遡灉<span class='krp-note'>即汴/水也</span>由灉而達河此一道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5439:5468'>　<span class='krp-note'>由灉達河/是東路</span>由泗之上源以遡泲由泲而達河此又一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5468:5497'>　道也<span class='krp-note'>由泲達河/是西路</span>是皆逆流而上者也張洎曰禹於滎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5497:5520'>　澤下分大河為隂溝引注東南以通淮泗至大梁浚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5520:5556'>　儀縣西北復分為二渠<span class='krp-note'>漢明帝時王景始作浚儀/渠循河溝故瀆故縣氏之</span>一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5556:5589'>　渠元經陽武中牟臺下為官渡水<span class='krp-note'>官渡在今中牟縣/曹操與袁紹相持</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5589:5618'>　<span class='krp-note'>於官渡/口即此</span>一渠始皇疏鑿以灌魏郡謂之鴻溝通考曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5618:5654'>　世言煬帝開汴渠以幸揚州<span class='krp-note'>隋大業三年詔𤼵河南/男女萬丁開汴水起滎</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5654:5681'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-14b' );" name="004-14b" class="pb">[004-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5681:5710'>　<span class='krp-note'>澤入淮/千餘里</span>考禹貢言堯都冀州居河下流而入都貢賦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5710:5733'>　重於用民力故每州必記入河之水獨淮與河無相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5733:5756'>　通之道求之故迹而不得乃疑汴渠自禹以來有之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5756:5786'>　不起於隋世既久逺或名鴻溝或名汴渠<span class='krp-note'>鴻溝在今/鄭州滎陽</span></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5786:5812'>　<span class='krp-note'>縣/</span>大概皆自河入淮故淮河引江湖之舟以達於冀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5812:5835'>　也今據後漢書則平帝時已有汴渠曰河汴决壞則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5835:5858'>　謂輸受之所也官渡直黄河也故袁曹相距沮授曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5858:5881'>　悠悠黄河吾其濟乎汴渠自禹來有之此不易之論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5881:5908'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0058', 'WYG', '004-15a' );" name="004-15a" class="pb">[004-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5908:5931'>　也又國䇿蘇子説魏王曰大王之地東有鴻溝陳汝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5931:5946'>　南則鴻溝之名亦不自秦始也</span><br/>
